bilingual.source: She has a job in a hotel.
Stay in a hotel for four nights.

bilingual.target: 这家酒店是由冰制成的。

bilingual.source: We are staying at the Grand Hotel.
The hotel is open till the end.
This is the nicest hotel in town.

yingyinNormal.en: I totally just saw what hotel he's staying at.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我刚才看到他下榻的酒店名字了。

yingyinNormal.en: She made me baby-proof the whole hotel. Someone's over-protective.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她让我把整个酒店都做防护了，某人过分保护了。

yingyinNormal.en: Then we'll go to a hotel. A hotel? Did you see The Shining?
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我们去酒店好了。酒店，你们没看过《闪灵》吗？

yingyinNormal.en: That's not me, I swear. You were in your hotel room taking a nap? Yes, I was in my hotel room.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是我，我发誓。你在你的酒店房间里小憩？是的，我待在酒店房间。

yingyinNormal.en: We have many wonderful things planned for you at the hotel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 酒店为您准备了很多娱乐项目。

yingyinNormal.en: The punishment for not paying your hotel bill in the UAE is jail.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在阿联酋，不付酒店费也要进监狱的。

yingyinNormal.en: We haven't decided. There's quite a good hotel in Ripon I know of.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们还没决定，里彭有间不错的酒店。

yingyinNormal.en: She's at hotel security and she needs a lawyer. I'm on it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她现在在酒店保安部，她需要律师我这就过去。

yingyinNormal.en: That's why we're not taking him there. And the hotel is full of guests.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以不能在那儿动手，酒店里又都是客人。

yingyinNormal.en: We're at the hotel. It's a free zone. Still. Out of respect.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们这是在酒店，自由场所。还是注意点吧，出于尊重。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, this is Ms. May, with the hotel. Wanted to have a quick word with you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，这位是梅女士，酒店的人，想跟你们聊两句。

yingyinNormal.en: Or sail into a sea of luxury at Burj Al Arab, a seven star hotel, whose graceful curves echo the traditional wooden vessels of the Gulf.
yingyinNormal.zh: 又或者到迪拜帆船酒店尽享奢华，这间七星级酒店的优美曲线，与波斯湾的传统木伐互相辉映。

yingyinNormal.en: No, it's all right, Randall. I'm just gonna go back to my hotel. Leave me alone, all right?
yingyinNormal.zh: 没事，兰德尔，我要回酒店了，别管我好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Or for a small fee, enjoy the luxurious amenities at one of the many private hotel beaches.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或于私人酒店沙滩，付小额费用享受豪华设施。

yingyinNormal.en: And it's so lonely at that hotel. I mean, I got this big suite all to myself, but I guess the bigger the hotel room, the emptier it can feel.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而且一个人住酒店太孤独了，我一个人住个大套间，但是房间越大，就越寂寞。

yingyinNormal.en: I do things, like I did in the hotel in Lowa. I can't even talk with you about it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我做的事，比如在爱荷华酒店的事，都没法跟你好好谈。

yingyinNormal.en: All in the police report. Rachel Posner was at the hotel that night.
yingyinNormal.zh: 都在警方报告里。Rachel Posner当晚也在那家酒店里。

yingyinNormal.en: But that hotel on that night? Well, now you sound like Ms. Skorsky talking.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可偏巧那晚去了那家酒店? 你这语气就像Skorsky小姐似得。

yingyinNormal.en: I meet him at his hotel first thing tomorrow morning, then we're on the go all day long.
yingyinNormal.zh: 明天一早我和他在酒店碰面，然后我们一整天都要到处跑。

yingyinNormal.en: It's more like how girls end up at a Best Western hotel with a 34-year-old guy named Luther.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实翘课的女生更有可能在酒店跟一个34岁的老头开房。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The really successful holders of such titles are those that do a great deal more than fill <highlight>hotel</highlight> bedrooms.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 真正成功的此类头衔持有者是那些除了填补酒店卧室之外还做了大量工作的人。
